name: Sadness
description: Our new puppy, Dexter chewed my Galaxy Note 8, Samsung  S-Pen and destroyed it. I had planned a whole series of GIFs based on this tool and now I can't follow through. Kinda hate the idea of getting a new phone, what if Dexter gets ahold of that? That'd be a shame. I've always been troubled by not always being able to follow through and this NFT journey on H=N is not much different. On top of all this, I recently bit into an apple and my fake tooth cracked and popped out, again. Just gotta ride this storm out and let the sadness pass.
